<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Welcome to PetsBook - Email Verification</title>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Hello, {{ name }}!</h1>
  
  <div class="welcome-section">
    <h2>Welcome to PetsBook!</h2>
    <p>Welcome to PetsBook - the social network for pet owners and their beloved animals.</p>
    <p>Your account has been successfully created and is ready to use.</p>
    <p>You can now:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Complete your profile</li>
      <li>Add your pets</li>
      <li>Connect with other pet owners</li>
      <li>Share your pet stories</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="verification-section">
    <h2>Email Verification</h2>
    <p>To complete your registration, please verify your email address by clicking the button below:</p>
    <p style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="{{ verifyUrl }}" 
         style="display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; 
                background-color: #4CAF50; color: white; 
                text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;">
        Verify Email Address
      </a>
    </p>
    <p>Or click this link: <a href="{{ verifyUrl }}">{{ verifyUrl }}</a></p>
    <p>This link will expire in 24 hours.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="contact-section">
    <p>Contact us:</p>
    <p>Phone: {{ Sender_Phone }}</p>
    <p>Email: {{ Sender_Email }}</p>
    <p>Address: {{ Company_Address }}</p>
    <p>Website: {{ Company_Website }}</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>